## 🔌 Pin Connections

### Motor Driver (L298N)

#### Motor 1
- IN1 → GPIO 27
- IN2 → GPIO 26
- ENA → GPIO 14

#### Motor 2
- IN3 → GPIO 33
- IN4 → GPIO 25
- ENB → GPIO 32

### Other Components

- Voltage Sensor → ESP32 ADC Pin (GPIO 34)
- Relay Module → GPIO 4 (Digital Output)

### Power

- ESP32 → 5V USB Supply
- Motor Driver → External Battery
- Common Ground for all components
